data.description: Lovely home on the edge of town.  There is a slider off kitchen and a slider off primary bedroom to a large (12 x 36) deck with fenced yard.  Bonus room in basement could also be used as 4th bedroom (no closet).  New flooring throughout most of home.  New kitchen appliances.  Extra-large 2 stall garage with walkdown access to lower level of house.
